3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>    。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》&quot;"},{"pid":"e609e6c98bd25377e45354f592ddc7c55ff71713","tid":1987295,"uid":196701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:46:07.000Z","msg":"連登仔日日都好痛苦"},{"pid":"e58274c9d1ddb93a1cd668a254c06f21f2c69a1d","tid":1987295,"uid":47160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:55:53.000Z","msg":"扮弱智係咪好易，只要答錯哂問卷就得? 洗唔洗照下個腦"},{"pid":"53c8668687b6cadf2ed8a5c938a87991361dc05a","tid":1987295,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e58274c9d1ddb93a1cd668a254c06f21f2c69a1d","tid":1987295,"uid":47160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:55:53.000Z","msg":"扮弱智係咪好易，只要答錯哂問卷就得? 洗唔洗照下個腦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:56:57.000Z","msg":"唔係，認真個人真係弱智同戇鳩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa5dc0a8c8e7d4ee6467387cdadec057e46a0a1","tid":1987295,"uid":185651,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T09:02:20.000Z","msg":"接連便是難懂的話，什麼「輕度弱智」，什麼「浪費資源」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：論壇內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"55289f3d44d991d5cc351a5dbfa5998d85a87533","tid":1987295,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9900d980a720b82088546534ab3c5309173650f2","tid":1987295,"uid":1834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T18:04:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，弱智會入到三大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T11:03:58.000Z","msg":"我唔係三大"},{"pid":"4c3953455ed233589c99f7be052477ca1149f5d9","tid":1987295,"uid":1834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55289f3d44d991d5cc351a5dbfa5998d85a87533","tid":1987295,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9900d980a720b82088546534ab3c5309173